name: eula Genshin Impact 原神 优菈
description:
通过调整lora模型的权重，自由控制从漫画到写实的风格转变

Freely control the style shift from caricature to realism by adjusting the weights of the lora model

如果您不能得到和图例相识的结果，请尝试降低lora模型的权重。调高则更接近手绘画风，调低则更接近真人画风

If you do not get a result that matches the illustration, try lowering the weight of the lora model. If you turn it up, it will be more similar to the hand-drawn style, if you turn it down, it will be closer to the real-life style.

并且，低权重时，会比较容易改变角色的衣着，但仍会受到角色衣着配色的影响。

And, at low weights, it will be easier to change a character's wardrobe, but it will still be influenced by the colour scheme of the character's wardrobe.

感谢你们的下载。

Thank you for your downloads.

modelVersions.name: eulav4-000082.safetensors
modelVersions.description:
一些经验分享，尽量用手绘风格的图像去训练lora模型，并在真人大模型上训练，如chilloumix等。这样你就可以自由地在在漫画风格和真人风格中切换了。

Some experience shared, try to train lora models with hand drawn style images and train on real people models such as chilloumix etc. This way you can freely switch between the comic style and the real life style.
